task-rest_bold.json.TaskDescription: During the resting state fMRI scan, participants were asked to relax with their eyes open, while a white cross-hair against a black background was projected on a screen. However, in a few cases, participants closed their eyes despite instructions to maintain them open. Eye status during the MRI scan was monitored via an eye tracker and is provided for each participant.
